    <!-- Slide 4: Mastery - Historical Context -->
    <div id="slide-4" class="slide">
        <div class="slide-content">
            <div class="slide-bg">
                <h2 class="text-5xl text-center mb-8 text-amber-300">ACHIEVING MASTERY: CONTEXT</h2>
                <p class="text-2xl mb-6">To earn top marks, your intel report must:</p>
                <ul class="list-none space-y-4 text-xl">
                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold text-3xl mr-4">&raquo;</span><span><span class="highlight">FULLY EXPLAIN</span> the circumstances that LED to the events. Think bigger picture.</span></li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold text-3xl mr-4">&raquo;</span><span>Connect your context to <span class="highlight">BOTH</span> documents, not just one.</span></li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold text-3xl mr-4">&raquo;</span><span>Show you know the whole story, the broader historical landscape.</span></li>
                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-red-500 font-bold text-3xl mr-4">&raquo;</span><span>Ensure <span class="highlight">ZERO INACCURACIES</span>. Bad intel fails the mission.</span></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-8 border-t-2 border-amber-300 pt-4">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-amber-300">PRO-TIP:</h3>
                    <p class="text-xl">Dedicate PARAGRAPH 1 solely to Historical Context. Stay organized, stay on target.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
